Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.30,0:26:32.53,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}您一定不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.08,0:26:41.44,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}因為我只有您
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.68,0:26:54.28,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}虛偽的童話 在我心中來回碰撞 噹噹作響
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.28,0:27:00.60,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}即便是沒有客人的舞臺
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.60,0:27:14.12,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}您亦帶着一副悲傷的神情 堅持起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.40,0:27:18.76,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}我愛着您的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.96,0:27:23.48,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}請讓我把您奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.68,0:27:31.20,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}這個得不到救贖的故事中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.52,0:27:36.04,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}一瞬間便好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.04,0:27:40.32,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}請您只注視我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.76,0:27:49.36,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}這便是我的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:55.24,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}不管觸摸多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.36,0:28:06.52,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}這份感情 依然無法傳達給您
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.84,0:28:12.28,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}但人是會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.28,0:28:15.92,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}因此您不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.92,0:28:26.96,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}不管命運受到了甚麼咀咒 我也要傳達給您
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.48,0:28:35.96,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}我愛着您的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.96,0:28:40.68,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}包括您的傷痕 您的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.88,0:28:48.36,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}您的罪惡 您的過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.60,0:28:58.00,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}我的一切都被您奪去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.00,0:29:05.52,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}現在 我依然是您的人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.60,0:29:12.28,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}所以 請留在我的身邊
